His impressive track record includes multiple appearances at the prestigious Hector Trophée, participating in the 2025, 2024, and 2022 editions of the tournament. While yet to claim victory in the Hector Trophée, Janne has consistently showcased his talent on the course, proving himself a formidable opponent.

Janne's dedication to the game is evident in his approach, and his performance at the Hector Trophée is a testament to his abilities. He is a player to watch in the years to come, with his refined skills and consistent improvement promising exciting performances.  We look forward to following his progress at this year's tournament.
